{"tid":2186966,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[半自動塔防] 有冇人一齊玩Mindustry","createTime":"2020-09-03T10:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T01:59:02.000Z","uid":18265,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd77f7a94c4fdcccc661ddead4e97f6b1c123aa","tid":2186966,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:28:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1127400/Mindustry/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1127400%2FMindustry%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hdE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=cb7c7d32\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1127400/Mindustry/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1127400/capsule_616x353.jpg?t=1586887170\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcdn-a.akamaihd.net%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F1127400%2Fcapsule_616x353.jpg%3Ft%3D1586887170&h=0c57bf66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMindustry 係隻沙盒塔防遊戲<br />\n玩家控制無人機採鑛同攻擊敵人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1127400/ss_a124f701b2eec73e5093ad147083fad1ac21ebbc.600x338.jpg?t=1586887170\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F1127400%2Fss_a124f701b2eec73e5093ad147083fad1ac21ebbc.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1586887170&h=77f96653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">玩法</span><br />\n每關玩家要起鑽頭同輸送帶等等建立生產線，採集鑛物<br />\n同時鋪路運彈藥畀前線炮台<br />\n每關攞到嘅鑛物可以用嚟升級科技樹<br />\n解鎖到其他防禦、運輸同生產嘅機械<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1127400/ss_9dd6927f900024e28b8ce78ecee22cbce346778b.600x338.jpg?t=1586887170\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F1127400%2Fss_9dd6927f900024e28b8ce78ecee22cbce346778b.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1586887170&h=f1932477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">遊戲模式</span><br />\n生存：建造砲塔來抵禦敵人入侵。生存愈久愈好，選擇發射您的核心並將您採集的資源用來研究新科技。為敵人頭目的到來做好準備。<br />\n攻擊：建造工廠並生產部隊來摧毀敵人的核心，同時保護自己的基地不受敵方單位的攻擊。建立各種不同類型的支援與攻擊單位來協助實現您的目標。<br />\nPvP：與最多四個不同團隊的玩家競爭摧毀其他人的核心。建立單位或直接用您的飛船攻擊其他人的基地。<br />\n沙盒：在資源無限而且無敵人威脅下盡情遊玩。使用僅在沙盒模式中才有的無限物品與液體來源<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1127400/ss_7287e4fee15671848312580fccb672930a9a331b.600x338.jpg?t=1586887170\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F1127400%2Fss_7287e4fee15671848312580fccb672930a9a331b.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1586887170&h=0c520768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1127400/ss_a124f701b2eec73e5093ad147083fad1ac21ebbc.600x338.jpg?t=1586887170\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F1127400%2Fss_a124f701b2eec73e5093ad147083fad1ac21ebbc.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1586887170&h=77f96653&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"814e395391a666a0fde539ec50eb5336d96abb12","tid":2186966,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f0d2bc10857b201ac5358e45beacbbc75732a7","tid":2186966,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:38:54.000Z","msg":"有冇co op mode？"},{"pid":"80b9140e965c0c3a838cdd3539c5630d3825fbbb","tid":2186966,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46f0d2bc10857b201ac5358e45beacbbc75732a7","tid":2186966,"uid":311223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:38:54.000Z","msg":"有冇co op mode？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"bff85215e1ae21d460a5d84713debf7f5e4ccbff","tid":2186966,"uid":44364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:45:42.000Z","msg":"見係手機移植就唔想玩lu<br />\n同埋有個外國人整左隻我覺得仲好玩嘅<br />\n網頁版free, steam有上架<br />\n為左支持佢 有免費我都買左 幾蚊<br />\n<br